radiographic_examinations.findings: Mild dependent bibasilar atelectasis in visualized lung fields, otherwise normal limits. Fluid-filled and dilated appendix measuring up to 1.3 cm with pelvic and right lower quadrant fat stranding and inflammatory changes. Normal liver, pancreas, spleen, adrenal glands, kidneys, and urinary structures. Moderate degree of heterogeneous free pelvic fluid.
